title: Cascading parameter values not displayed properly in HTML viewer
description: Cascading parameter values are not being displayed correctly in the HTML viewer.
OB: When selecting the first parameter value, the second parameter value in the same cascading parameter group should be displayed, but it is not displayed.
EB: The issue can be reproduced by previewing the attached design file in the HTML viewer and then clicking on the 'change parameter' button.
SR: To replicate the issue: 1. Preview the attached design file in the HTML viewer. 2. Click on the 'change parameter' button in the HTML viewer.
